In May 2003, after the review of the expert group, it entered the ranks of the first batch of demonstration high schools in Liaoning Province.


Huludao No. 1 senior middle school is one of the top 100 key middle schools in China, ranking 84th in China (2011, 2010), a key middle school and model school in Liaoning Province, and a high school directly under Huludao Education Bureau.
Since the founding of new China, nearly 30000 outstanding graduates have started here, moved in all directions, become the pillars of society, and made important contributions to the construction of material and spiritual civilization of the motherland. In the hearts of citizens, it is the "Tsinghua garden" in the hearts of Huludao citizens.


